Text: I see a couple of other episodes on here saying they're eztv but they're fake. Episodes 8&9. I know this ones for real just thought I'd let you know, looks like someone's trying to do a dodgy on you EZ...thanks for all the U/L's cheers

@oigveh - ettv is another reliable (green skull) uloader. Similar quality to good ol' ez and most of the same shows. Sometimes gets them on TPB a little earlier, but ez and et can both be trusted to deliver the goods!
